PREREQUISITES:
• Laravel Breeze React starter kit installed
• OTPz package: composer require benbjurstrom/otpz
• Migrations run: php artisan migrate

ROUTES (add to routes/web.php):
```php
use App\Http\Controllers\Auth\OtpzController;

Route::middleware('guest')->group(function () {
    Route::get('otpz/{id}', [OtpzController::class, 'get'])
        ->name('otpz.get')->middleware('signed');
    Route::post('otpz/{id}', [OtpzController::class, 'store'])
        ->name('otpz.post')->middleware('signed');
});
```

USAGE:
Update your login controller to use SendOtp action and redirect to $otp->url

Full docs: https://github.com/benbjurstrom/otpz

